'''Leopold''' is a camel living on the [[Island of the White Leaf Desert]]. He is seen near the [[Hacienda]] with his [[grobo]] owner. Leopold claims to be imported. He loves sand roses which he gets from his owner.

Leopold has no role in the game, and talking with him is not vital.

